Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know Eto Sensei, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Nodame's Sensei is Tanioka Sensei, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmmm....could he possibly mistake his student?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't joke around!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhhh....Gorota...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear anything about yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from Tanioka Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aryaa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show that I can bring out your piano talent fully
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after being buried for these 3 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be thankful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's begin the lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.12,0:00:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, play for me the piece you've played before,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or one that you like, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick, sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.63,0:00:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what's this? Music Score?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fart Exercise...What's this??
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the piece I've played before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.04,0:00:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haaaa???
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:00:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to be used for exercise in the kindergarten
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:00:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with Tanioka Sensei, I plan to complete it by the time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of education internship, including the body movements too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck were you doing, up to now??
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! Classic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play classical piece as normally!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "normally"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Chopin, or Liszt!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must know even if only one piece, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Okay....Mary-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What piece is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is not a kindergarten or a small music lesson in town!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a MUSIC ACADEMY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover you're already a student whom I selected!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot play around for even a second....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PLAYING AROUND, YOU SAID??!\N(she suddenly speaks with an accent like him)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NODAME IS DOING IT SERIOUSLY !
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mary-san's....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT'S WRONG WITH IT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NODAME'S STUDYING PROPERLY!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't address me with "Omae"\N(="you", but rude)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heeeeeh???
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Tanioka Hajime ]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanioka Sensei!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun, you entered the wrong room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the instructor suddenly change?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so I haven't told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Eto Sensei's request, he said he wanted\Nto be your instructor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it simply changed just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because I know once he said it he wouldn't listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he has more authority than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he also seems to be enthusiastic in doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, I thought it would be interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the combination of you and Eto-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's NOT interesting at all!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, we are also having a lesson right now,\Nplease leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your instructor is not me anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, shall we begin from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When and where are we going to perform, and what\Npiece shall we play?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, we should decide first where to practice.\NMoreover we don't have enough people yet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have to contact more people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if we won't get any assistance from school,\Nwe'll have to gather them by ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a student orchestra and semi-pro too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I got excited
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got into A-Oke!\NServe you right!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two string people added....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NFrom your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A smiling face with a wild imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we continue this at another place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking party for the new orchestra
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[No-name Orchestra]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyora! It's been a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Masumi-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katayama-kun! Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had not met since the Dream Music Festival, had we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like that they all know each other, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we can get along well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, even Masumi-chan too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the ones who know the Conductor are\Nonly us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun, do you like Sibelius?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last year I played Sibelius....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masumi-chan, Chiaki's in danger!!\NGo, go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoahhhh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never changes, Masumi-chan, always in high-tension
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Chaiki-kun's conducting soon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they said you're the only Stresemann's pupil, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's good if today we can decide first\Nthe piece we are going to play
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun, do you have a particular piece\Nyou want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have thought about it, but I have several...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to do it, I'd like to do an a "hade"\None, gathering more people to join us\N(= attention-catching)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my opinion, with this number of people,\Nit's also good to do a classic....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, like playing Mozart and the likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, rather than Mozart, Haydn is better for it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I feel strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely different from S-Oke's drinking party
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is calm and mature...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good...I feel relaxed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bruckner's Symphony no 9 is impressive, it'll be good, I think
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ 30 minutes later ]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be Beethoven!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a blink of an eye, it turned into\Na scene I'm used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And within just 30 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone easily gets drunk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I have a piece I'd like us to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, me too!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahler's "Symphony of A Thousand"!!\N(=Symphony no 8)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MARRIAGE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Symphony of A Thousand..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne, Chiaki-kun, for now, why don't we\Ndo a concerto for one of our pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah good, there's someone with the right mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing....Yes, a concerto will be good
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of doing it too
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of good soloists in this Oke
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True. Because of that....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's do a cello concerto
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of course, with me as the soloist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flute concerto! I'll be the soloist!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, don't fight over it!\NLet's do a violin concerto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right! And I'll be the soloist!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DIVORCE!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine put aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everybody has the confidence of being the soloist?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about a contrabass concerto? Contrabass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosh! Coming to this, let's let Chiaki-kun\Ndecide over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, you may not bear a grudge over this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haiiiii!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:07:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contrabass! Contrabass!\NViolin! Violin!! Contrabass!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK I decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we do an oboe concerto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Kuroki-kun as the soloist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Chiaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't come here today
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine said that tonight they were going to have a\Ndrinking party for the new orchestra
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so perhaps Chiaki-san went there too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new orchestra?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Nodame-chan is not the mascot girl anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne, would you like to eat something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the right time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne, try this!\NGnocchi simmered in Mabo stew!\N(weird! Italian with Chinese flavor)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today Nodame's going home..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Nodame is strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not as usual, she's really weird
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always weird, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma....ma....ma....ma....ma....mabo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't eat Mabo as usual!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she turned to look like a ggghost!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha??
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laterz!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame was acting weird, my Dad said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She came to my house, but without eating anything,\Nshe went staggering home,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame not eating meal, is it THAT weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is my Dad an idiot or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosh! Shall we go to the second\Ndrinking place now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun, you'll go to the second drinking\Nplace too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for me to....\N(he meant he'd go home)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, let's go, let's go!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki Senpai....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ME
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ME
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CAN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame Cantabile\NLesson 7
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,http://s-projects.org
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best with your practice!\NSmooch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "uwaki", OK?\N(=cheating by having an affair with another)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly!\NFor me, there's only you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikuchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hitotsuma Megumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitotsuma??!! (=someone's legal wife)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi Sezan!\N(=Suzanne? Susan? LOL)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to practice now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cheating on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AMAZING!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama's going to make an orchestra?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are that Oke's members,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they said they were\Ngoing to practice in our school
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody seems to be excellent students\Nfrom other Academies...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Araaa! You didn't know it??
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that it's Chiaki-kun's Oke???
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to do anymore with that kind of guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that alright with you? To let such people\Npractice in our school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimura??
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were at the same Music High School
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was well-known for being extremely good at violin,\Nbut he was also extremely weak
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was often bullied!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not him, but you, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the number two in this Academy..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! Did you see Noda Megumi from Piano Division?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have not seen her yet today..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NODA MEGUMI!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,COME OUT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you play truant you'll have to repeat this year!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand??!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Chiaki-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we should play it a bit stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then from here we can play it a little softer ...I think
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in that case, the change from the second theme\Nwould be hard to append
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall I make it crispier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's start from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you two sitting there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you so!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Oboe Concerto only needs 35 players!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It only needs 18 violin players,\Nwith first and second violins combined.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It needs two Contrabass
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why for this piece, you don't have\Nany part to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! He found us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you choose such a piece?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How silly, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the timpani isn't used, so bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mozart, Oboe Concerto in C Major
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The piece is Allegro Aperto
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it must be Kuroki-kun's confidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that has chosen this most famous concerto,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which has always be the set-piece for any\Noboe player competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has high technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,doing it in minute details,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unshaking spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how can I say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai...he's like a samurai, Kuroki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, all are excellent players
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They also have good intuition
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This orchestra is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the first day playing the whole piece too
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also because these days we're just practising for\Nthe competition, and always skipped orchestras
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, everybody remains in that final selection
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as expected, Chiaki-kun's really amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered how good he was
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but his guidance was precise, and his\Nunderstanding of the piece is also high
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.91,0:13:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be studying a lot.\NAs expected, he's Stresemann's pupil!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skillful
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all more skillful than me..\NExtremely skillful
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people are frequenters of competitions, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't participate in competitions because\Nmy goal is to enter professional Oke...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was also chosen as S-Oke's Concert Master
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I also could get into A-Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have such a leisure time to complain,\Nwhy don't you use it to practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but acting like a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Chiaki!\NPlease decide the next piece quickly!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course a piece I can participate in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wanted to prepare it in advance,\Nand make everybody say "WOW!~"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koitsu's preparation in advance doesn't matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you don't decide it quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there won't be enough time\Nto make the publicity either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Koitsu"?? Hah??\N(=that person, but rude)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Ryuu-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Publicity? We haven't even decided\Non the Hall yet....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimura-kun! We seem to be able to reserve\NTokyo Symphony Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really??
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bit connection with that Hall, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concerning this sort of thing, Chiaki-kun is umm..ignorant,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or ummm...not very sensitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or "Music-Only Idiot"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I took over the matters related to accounting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:14:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEY WAIT A MINUTE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo Symphony Hall??
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, how many persons does it accomodate??
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll perform in Tokyo Symphony Hall as a nameless Oke??
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However hard we advertise, we can't possibly ....\N(the hall is too big!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about advertising, leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma Manabu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to make an official public notice in Classic Life?\NOf course we'll ask for a payment, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy it! One full page!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you two here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a phone call
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saying that Chiaki-kun made an orchestra with\Nwonderful members...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was an anonymous call.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anonymous?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! If we're going to make a public notice,\NAnonymous?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! If we're going to make a public notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we must think of the Oke's name first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have thought about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What....what's that?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rising Star Orchestra?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abbreviated: "R.S Oke"!\NIt's a good name, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a name my Dad and I thought of whole night long!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treat it with care, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why must it be you and your Dad who thought of it??!\NReally embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rising stars..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the shining greatest treasures that suddenly\Nappeared in the black darkness....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the twinkling stars of hope which we behold\Nin the sky we gaze up above....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, with the music you play...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even the twilight of the Gods  can also\Nbe changed into Hope
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flap your wings freely in this vast universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The name has quite a deep meaning,"\Nthat's what he was saying
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in fact I didn't give it any meaning so\Ndeep to that extent....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go home, as I still have to decide\Nthe piece we're going to play next to Mozart's
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment, Chiaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Stresemann's latest new release\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Stresemann's latest new release
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend in Germany sent it to me.\NYou can have it if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Chiaki-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is! Stamina Food Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let Nodame-chan eat them
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai's going to conduct Mozart??
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Mozart is pink color!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the image color in Nodame's mind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki Senpai conducting pink?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you finish eating, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that news about Nodame becoming a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, she talks a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,eat a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about her for completely nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh what about you..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's your study going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your piano practice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact Nodame..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a while I won't be able to accompany you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,therefore practice properly by yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! Yes, next time I'll deliver food\Nto your orchestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will lemons dipped in honey again be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come! Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eeeh, why???
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask. Anyway, don't come!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Oke is not for playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's the only thing I can do in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh??
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since such good members already gathered
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want cause strange gossips
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than pink...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's dull silver?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that for Mozart's piece
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps it would be better to have a little\Nmore cheerfulness and warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's take a break for ten minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Kuroki-kun, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here on this place..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bring you miso soup and rice balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...please help yourselves with these...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, No---Nodame??
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[It's being used by R.S Oke!!]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! I told you not to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm just delivering this, and I'll go home immmediately
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! I'll greet everybody in the Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to greet them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm your w...wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today you have a lesson, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanioka Sensei caught a cold, so....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then I'll call him to wish him a speedy recovery
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaa....ahhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today Tanioka Sensei....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with his family...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,went to Mexico...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, something's strange indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're always strange, you never skip your lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier what you said about this place..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're in the middle of something, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaaa...not at all, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not in the middle of anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, you're someone from Chiaki Senpai's Oke, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some food here. If you like, please\Nhave some....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice balls....and miso soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best with your practise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gomen kudasai! *bows*\N(=super polite good bye)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(See how she walks, it's like a Kyoto dancer/geisha\Nin kimono, LOL, it's NOT normal!)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*bows*
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl..Later I'll sure make her have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*bows"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun...\NIs that girl...\N*bows"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun...\NIs that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha? No, she's my Kohai in Piano Division\N(Kohai= opposite of Senpai)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N...Noda Megumi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda....Megumi.....chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So skillful!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:21:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it makes you feel down, why don't you stop\Ncoming here to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazinnnggg~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to produce such sounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me as your pupil!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haa??
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me private lessons!\NHaa??
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me private lessons!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only whenever you have the time is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you with any food you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will massage your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why??
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have teachers of your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're much much more skillful\Nthan my teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suki da!\N(I love you/ I love it)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Kiyora's violin!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I start the practise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai! You can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start from the beginning all the way through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.39,0:22:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier this Oke was dull silver...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now it became pink Mozart....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:22:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Nodame..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.38,0:22:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you *bows*
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! Gokigen yo! *bows*\N(again very very polite greeting)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.59,0:23:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My husband is always indebted to you....\N*bows* *bows* *bows*
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame's instructor changed to Harisen??
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, so suddenly??
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the two of you play Rachmaninoff some time ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.92,0:23:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.81,0:23:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that Eto Sensei seems to like\NNodame-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he listened to that ...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.26,0:23:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyaboo!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WAIT, NODA!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today I don't feel well, so....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you running now?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hahaha, wow, so much excitement...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two won't be able to get along well..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.70,0:23:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's in order to do something with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.05,0:23:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Tanioka Sensei would have done it yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.32,0:23:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not the kind of teacher who has enough initiative
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.63,0:23:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to bring out enough initiative\Nfrom a student who hasn't enough intiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since students are important customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.39,0:23:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cooperate and make an effort\Nto help them achieve their dreams or hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:23:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, for these 3 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up guiding her, cooperating in her composing\Nthose pieces such as "Mojya-mojya Suite" and "Fart Exercise"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.39,0:24:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,viewed from my policy as an instructor,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.08,0:24:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if Noda-kun doesn't want it, I don't want to hand her\Nto Eto-kun either!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.43,0:24:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.45,0:24:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that lately something changed in her....Noda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.64,0:24:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although she herself might not realize it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.33,0:24:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something has changed....
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I wish to see....
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.53,0:24:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a separate individual...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.93,0:24:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.07,0:24:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ojisan is stuck there
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.55,0:24:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miaouwww....
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.54,0:24:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Nodame Sensei's Guide Book]
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.51,0:25:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Concerning the chorus"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.41,0:25:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Study of musical instruments"\N"Concerning playing musical instruments"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.97,0:25:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Scale Practise"\NPractise of strong and weak sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.44,0:25:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.95,0:25:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the right time! Let's go home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.69,0:25:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame wants to go to supermarket to buy\Nmaterials for tomorrow's food delivery
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.13,0:25:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.56,0:25:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until when do you intend to skip your lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.63,0:25:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow Tanioka Sensei is going to..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.08,0:25:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your instructor is Harisen
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.22,0:25:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I attend the other classes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.56,0:25:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like children education...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.01,0:25:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you don't suit that job
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.47,0:25:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't suit to be a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.95,0:25:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.15,0:25:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you possibly advise children for education?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.84,0:25:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be disrespected and bullied by the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.18,0:25:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way you can't be a teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.20,0:26:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame will be a kindergarten teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.25,0:26:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were a parent....
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.86,0:26:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only to you, I certainly won't entrust my kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.60,0:26:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today Nodame will go home by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.33,0:26:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.92,0:26:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-oh, please do that favour for me!\NI'll go home by myself too!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.97,0:26:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's live separately too!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.58,0:26:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's divorce!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.52,0:26:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(I noticed this is Roppongi Hills)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.04,0:26:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.98,0:26:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely suitable to be a music performer....
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.88,0:26:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the way she is now, it can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.00,0:26:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much talent she has...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.45,0:26:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but as long as she does not wish it to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.45,0:27:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I drag and pull her up...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.06,0:27:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the end, the thing which can change her..
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.04,0:27:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be her own effort to get better....
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.22,0:27:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the person from Chiaki Senpai's Oke...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.18,0:27:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda...Megumi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.68,0:27:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.24,0:27:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.77,0:27:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh....
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.00,0:27:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kuroki Yasunori from Morimitsu Music Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.28,0:27:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food for lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.35,0:27:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it, don't mention it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.23,0:27:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That...and this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.61,0:27:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was taking a walk outside,\NI saw it accidentally in a flower shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.46,0:27:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.36,0:27:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily of the Valley's flower message?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.83,0:27:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Purity". "Pure love"....
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.01,0:27:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is as my gratitude for the rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.20,0:28:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.79,0:28:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.63,0:28:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is there still anymore practice for the orchestra?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.34,0:28:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, no...the practise is already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.91,0:28:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since there's no class today and I have\Nnothing to do, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.57,0:28:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.72,0:28:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of shaving some reeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.98,0:28:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.36,0:28:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For clarinets and saxophones, they sell reeds which they\Ncan use without having to shave first
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.07,0:28:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for oboe, we have to shave the reeds by ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.83,0:28:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heeeei.....so this is a reed?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.30,0:28:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It needs a lot of work..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.21,0:28:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with that included, I like oboe
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.66,0:28:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lovable because it needs some work on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.76,0:28:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.89,0:28:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people tend to think of it as a plain thing in\Nthe orchestrea
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.54,0:28:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People tend to think of it as a plain thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.47,0:28:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ah...hmm...yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.95,0:28:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Nodame likes the sound of oboe
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.14,0:28:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice it is to be in an orchestra...\NSeems to be so enjoyable
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.01,0:28:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi-chan's a piano player?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.53,0:28:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.66,0:28:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it enjoyable?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.13,0:28:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh it's enjoyable!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.40,0:29:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I like piano
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.15,0:29:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.42,0:29:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show that I can bring out your piano talent fully
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.26,0:29:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you aim higher?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.96,0:29:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't suit to be a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.47,0:29:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroki-kun, do you aim to be a professional?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.05,0:29:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or aim for a higher goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.08,0:29:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.17,0:29:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, to be a professional is my target
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.25,0:29:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's strange, isn't it, if I, who want to be a\Nkindergarten teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.75,0:29:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aim for a higher goal like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.06,0:29:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what Megumi-chan means\Nby aiming for a "higher" goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.61,0:29:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but doing music,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.96,0:29:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply if we can perform well, we feel happy
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.98,0:29:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if we can perform even better, won't we perhaps be\Nable to enjoy it better as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.35,0:29:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, to aim higher is....
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.07,0:29:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps to enjoy music purely....
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.90,0:29:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't Megumi-chan think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.75,0:30:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.29,0:30:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your girlfriend!! What's wrong with her??
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.08,0:30:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of human is she??
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.08,0:30:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's naturally hentai, isn't she?\N(=abnormal, weird, peverted)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.64,0:30:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my girlfriend, but yes, she's hentai
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.36,0:30:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't she take lessons like a normal person?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.00,0:30:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she's hentai, she's a Music Academy student!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.79,0:30:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you also do not give lessons like a normal person
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.62,0:30:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haa?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.44,0:30:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no other person giving lessons holding\Na harisen like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.04,0:30:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not just a harisen
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.44,0:30:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the form of my love
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.36,0:30:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking again about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.91,0:30:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why is Nodame running away from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.62,0:30:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Harisen is strict,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.46,0:30:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her rejection is way too strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.11,0:30:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but.....
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.27,0:31:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today I'll part with this harisen
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.18,0:31:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to repeat similar mistake I\Nmade with you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.04,0:31:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However hentai she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.62,0:31:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.60,0:31:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let go of the student I picked up by myself anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.65,0:31:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.37,0:31:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.33,0:31:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waaa, Puri Gorota figure with candy,\Nthe one costing 350 yen??
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.72,0:31:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wahhh, Riona!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.02,0:31:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waaah! Papa! Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.22,0:31:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waah! Mama!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.07,0:31:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, ???
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.33,0:32:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...but where's Kazuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.54,0:32:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuoooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.66,0:32:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got Kazuo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.59,0:32:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Eto Kozo]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.16,0:32:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today it's with lunch-box attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.92,0:32:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't run away! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.00,0:32:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I already threw away my harisen!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.06,0:32:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.05,0:32:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.24,0:32:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing on my waist
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.32,0:32:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.36,0:32:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also apologize for yelling at you that day
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.50,0:32:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.02,0:32:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, please take your lessons normally
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.03,0:32:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anooo...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.66,0:32:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.76,0:33:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing I'd like to request
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.45,0:33:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Request?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.80,0:33:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fart Agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.89,0:33:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1. To cooperate in the body exercise of "Fart Exercise"\Nuntil its completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.00,0:33:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2. Never hit me anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.57,0:33:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more than one!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.69,0:33:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eto Kozo
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.14,0:33:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's think of a good exercise
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.76,0:33:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Here we concluded the "Fart Exercise Agreement"!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.57,0:33:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hee...okay, first I'll eat this obento...\N(=lunch box)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.17,0:33:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No....eat it after the lesson is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.11,0:33:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fart Exercise!! Ooo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.54,0:33:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK start!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.65,0:33:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}<c:#FF80C0>Let's release it energetically,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.61,0:33:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}<c:#FF80C0>Let's release it with a good sound{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.69,0:33:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.53,0:33:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}<c:#FF80C0>Do Re Mi Fa Boo Boo Boo Boo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.83,0:33:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}<c:#FF80C0>Waaaa!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.95,0:33:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After this is completed,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.20,0:33:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}<c:#FF80C0>Big fart, small fart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.23,0:33:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the real lesson...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.18,0:33:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}<c:#FF80C0>...all are the same farts anyway{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.80,0:34:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will start!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.84,0:34:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing while doing it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.91,0:34:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}<c:#FF80C0>Put your hands on your hip{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.92,0:34:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}<c:#FF80C0>Okay let's fart now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.29,0:34:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}<c:#FF80C0>Hey! Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.21,0:34:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}<c:#FF80C0>Boooooooo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.10,0:34:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.24,0:34:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, something fell off...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.48,0:34:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way to handle Noda Megumi
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.37,0:34:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1. For the time being, Puri Gorota
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.29,0:34:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2.  For the time being, lunch box
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.14,0:34:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3. For the time being, let her do it as she likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.21,0:34:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aryaa? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.23,0:34:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki Shinichi
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.84,0:34:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puri Gorota? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.27,0:34:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, maybe it's also good to bait her\Nwith lunch box
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.66,0:34:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.83,0:34:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, let her play the piano as she likes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.83,0:34:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, despite saying this and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.35,0:34:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's the one most worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.87,0:34:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.56,0:34:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, shall we do it from the start of this.....
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.03,0:34:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going??!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.26,0:34:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Wait!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.45,0:34:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.59,0:34:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't I given you the bait?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.90,0:35:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still selecting the piece to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.44,0:35:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are several candidates to choose from,\Nbut none of them really strikes me as the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.10,0:35:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.17,0:35:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pamphlet of Tokyo Symphony Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.71,0:35:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It includes the seating map, so I think it\Nwill make a good reference
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.91,0:35:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.75,0:35:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Saiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.32,0:35:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to do it until this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.83,0:35:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally you found it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.69,0:35:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you can do in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.62,0:35:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to think that unless I went abroad,\Nthere would be no meaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.19,0:35:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the best place for classic was Europe,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.28,0:35:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that however good I would be judged in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.15,0:35:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wouldn't be able to reach the peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.61,0:35:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now....
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.61,0:35:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! What about the splitting up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.77,0:35:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The living separately?? The divorce??
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.70,0:35:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than that, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.52,0:36:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you can't go abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.03,0:36:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...how come did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.47,0:36:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it from rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.54,0:36:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.98,0:36:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be eavesdropping, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.12,0:36:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you go abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.92,0:36:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you suffering from ecology syndrome?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.11,0:36:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or have you done something bad that you can't\Nmake a passport?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.93,0:36:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is, leave it alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.26,0:36:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.25,0:36:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're afraid of getting on a plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.30,0:36:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's true, isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.12,0:36:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you didn't go to study abroad,\Nbut continue to the Graduate School, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.62,0:36:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine with me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.69,0:36:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm thinking of doing whatever I can here
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.77,0:36:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with that Oke
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.19,0:36:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.44,0:36:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, study, study!!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.50,0:36:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.99,0:36:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aryaa? Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.15,0:37:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Brahms Symphony no 1"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.60,0:37:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, please read this..
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.15,0:37:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brahms Symphony no 1
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.05,0:37:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This piece is said to have consume the time\Nspanning 20 years until its completion:
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.71,0:37:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brahms' first Symphony.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.24,0:37:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.74,0:37:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, if you hear this magnificent Symphony\Nof Brahms'
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.33,0:37:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps you will understand that in those 20 years he\Nhad not wasted even one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.15,0:37:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki! I was saying that you should immerse yourself\Nmore into the music!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.78,0:38:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't notice something important
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.21,0:38:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The important thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.60,0:38:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how seriously you and this piece are facing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.17,0:38:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.67,0:38:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,half-heartedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.34,0:38:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.36,0:38:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.42,0:38:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.64,0:38:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.29,0:38:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.02,0:38:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,violin...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.17,0:38:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.96,0:38:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.40,0:38:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no more time to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.68,0:38:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.98,0:38:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be engrossed in Brahms' world
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.89,0:39:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided that on December the 3rd,\Nat Tokyo Symphony Hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.92,0:39:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.30,0:39:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will perform in Rising Star Orchestra's public performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.65,0:39:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to enter into Brahms right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.29,0:39:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so everyone get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.00,0:39:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.75,0:39:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally our turn came!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.02,0:39:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK let's do it!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.23,0:39:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry, sorry, I'm late...\Nbecause my lesson took a bit longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.03,0:39:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.03,0:39:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it has began already...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.86,0:39:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.68,0:39:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! Be more concentrated in doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.19,0:39:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?? What's that?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.22,0:39:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...I understand that you have practise\Nfor the competition..
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.38,0:39:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for the Concert Master to be late???
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.47,0:39:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's free, but because of the competition,\Nthe Oke's practice time has already diminished
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.35,0:39:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all of you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.02,0:39:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.32,0:39:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't really put your mind in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.90,0:39:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for now, we can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.34,0:39:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the competition is over,\Nour future depend on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.49,0:39:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I also depend my future on this Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.36,0:40:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.65,0:40:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, this is not a professional Oke,\Nhow can you depend your future on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.34,0:40:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, everybody, what do you have in mind\Nparticipating in this Oke??
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.01,0:40:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.92,0:40:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,well, to be able to perform with\Nexcellent members of the same generation
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.44,0:40:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will make a good experience
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.72,0:40:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will be an incentive, and furthermore..
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.08,0:40:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.33,0:40:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.39,0:40:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that with these members,\Nif we do it together with Chiaki-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.21,0:40:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to do an amazing job...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.94,0:40:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right??
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.89,0:40:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of doing something amazing,\Nsomething which can match a professional Oke
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.16,0:40:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone thinks the same way, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.52,0:40:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we become popular, when people will\Nalways come to see us, we can earn money,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.74,0:40:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and can continue this Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.18,0:40:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same as a professional Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.53,0:40:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think ...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.07,0:40:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's this Oke, then it'll certainly be able to become so!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.80,0:40:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.29,0:40:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's an orchestra that will last forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.54,0:40:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.23,0:40:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I think that's a very good dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.54,0:40:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm returning to Boston in spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.37,0:40:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.10,0:41:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, sooner or later, I intend to return\Nto Vienna
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.39,0:41:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I want to do something amazing\Nin this Oke,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.05,0:41:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my dream for the future is to be based in Vienna,\Nwhile performing worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.86,0:41:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun must be thinking the same, right? Naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.02,0:41:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a matter of course! He's Stresemann's pupil!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.51,0:41:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still in Japan, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.79,0:41:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Chiaki-kun, he'll sure win in the competitions\Nabroad!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.83,0:41:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Naturally"??
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.13,0:41:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.38,0:41:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather than wanting to be in a member of an orchestra,\Nwe wish to be a soloist.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.42,0:41:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought without doubt that this is just a\None-time performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.63,0:41:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To gather periodically is good....
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.75,0:41:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but about professional Oke, are you serious??
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.37,0:41:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course....to go that far...no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.35,0:41:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.34,0:41:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brahms Symphony no 1, First Movement,\Nfirst synchronization, let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.89,0:42:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, you all!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.85,0:42:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you all laugh at Mine??!!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.74,0:42:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I..
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.82,0:42:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody will go their own ways....
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.98,0:42:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough for today
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.46,0:42:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No..
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.32,0:43:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop our practice, until the competition is over
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.19,0:43:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck in the competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.64,0:43:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Chiaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.69,0:43:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.67,0:43:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's something that's clearly understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.61,0:43:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That everyone will leave
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.90,0:43:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is something I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.83,0:44:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.28,0:44:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.14,0:44:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the plane accident at that time.....
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.87,0:44:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.46,0:44:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the first time I see..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.43,0:44:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a human being?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.21,0:45:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Beta version, I made it in a rush,\Nsorry for any mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.90,0:45:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the last 20%, I subbed it while watching another\Ndorama The Glass Slipper on TV (Korean subbed in Japanese)\NSorry if I messed up
